'''''The Wild Chase''''' is a [[Warner Bros. Animation]] [[Looney Tunes]] short featuring [[Sylvester]], [[Wile E. Coyote and Road Runner|Wile E. Coyote, Road Runner]] and [[Speedy Gonzales]]. It was directed by [[Friz Freleng]] and [[Hawley Pratt]], and was released February 27, 1965


==Plot synopsis==
{{spoilers}}
Sylvester and Wile E. Coyote combine forces in an attempt to catch their speedy nemeses the Road Runner and Speedy Gonzales, with predictable results.

